{"tid":50682,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我睇蛇仔明睇到上晒癮","createTime":"2016-12-22T15:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T23:23:58.000Z","uid":5846,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"608c7e5236393cf1170e0658b62b011330d62bd2","tid":50682,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"近日我先開始睇佢嘅片，每次睇完都好開心，但亦都有少少感觸<br />\n<br />\n我十幾年都無老豆陪（我好細果陣佢走左去包二奶）<br />\n<br />\n一直都覺得童年有缺失<br />\n<br />\n睇到蛇仔明同臭fing玩，成日都會幻想自己有個咁嘅老豆。其實幸福有個錫自己嘅親人就夠。<br />\n<br />\n做人老豆嘅，唔洗賺好多錢，比足夠嘅時間仔女，做到蛇仔明咁，係我眼中已經係滿分。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b9bce7d6a6d8c63e32fc3b83849499fc66e97b","tid":50682,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"922eaa8aa68bf97b91b052728b5aa351e5a023ee","tid":50682,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:51:51.000Z","msg":"Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫書溫到好大壓力會上utube睇佢地既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起以前細個都好似臭fing咁成日叫阿媽買玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會周圍行下反狗城個d玩具店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edd1b92f28a626a47440bd1309873f70127854d","tid":50682,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫書溫到好大壓力會上utube睇佢地既片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗返起以前細個都好似臭fing咁成日叫阿媽買玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又會周圍行下反狗城個d玩具店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個永遠都係自己行玩具店<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e838ff5bfa9ab968f5fe473f2cecaef58e341c5","tid":